<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Game Feel Database</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:        #0d0d0f;
      --surface:   #141417;
      --border:    #222228;
      --accent:    #c8f04a;
      --accent-dim:#8aaa2e;
      --text:      #e8e8ec;
      --muted:     #7a7a88;
      --axis-f:    #4af0c8;
      --axis-s:    #4ab4f0;
      --axis-d:    #f04a6a;
      --axis-i:    #c84af0;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(13,13,15,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-status {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .status-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      animation: pulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.3; }
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-headline {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero-headline em {
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .hero-body {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 560px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-body strong {
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cta-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #0d0d0f;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .cta-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-dim); }

    .cta-secondary {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* AXIS STRIP */
    .axis-strip {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .axis-track {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      animation: scroll-left 30s linear infinite;
      width: max-content;
    }

    .axis-strip:hover .axis-track { animation-play-state: paused; }

    @keyframes scroll-left {
      0% { transform: translateX(0); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    .axis-tag {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
      border: 1px solid;
      white-space: nowrap;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .axis-tag.f { color: var(--axis-f); border-color: var(--axis-f); }
    .axis-tag.s { color: var(--axis-s); border-color: var(--axis-s); }
    .axis-tag.d { color: var(--axis-d); border-color: var(--axis-d); }
    .axis-tag.i { color: var(--axis-i); border-color: var(--axis-i); }

    /* HOW IT WORKS */
    .section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .section-label::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .step {
      background: var(--surface);
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .step-num {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .step-title {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .step-body {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* PROFILE DEMO */
    .demo {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .demo-title {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .demo-game {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .axes-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .axis-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.3rem;
    }

    .axis-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .axis-label span { color: var(--text); }

    .axis-bar-track {
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--border);
      position: relative;
    }

    .axis-bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      transition: width 0.6s ease;
    }

    /* PILLARS */
    .pillars {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 2px;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .pillar {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .pillar-name {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .pillar-name.f { color: var(--axis-f); }
    .pillar-name.s { color: var(--axis-s); }
    .pillar-name.d { color: var(--axis-d); }
    .pillar-name.i { color: var(--axis-i); }

    .pillar-desc {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* NOTIFY */
    .notify-section {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .notify-inner {
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .notify-headline {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .notify-sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .notify-form {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .notify-input {
      flex: 1;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-right: none;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .notify-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
    .notify-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }

    .notify-btn {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #0d0d0f;
      border: none;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .notify-btn:hover { background: var(--accent-dim); }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .footer-note {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .notify-form { flex-direction: column; }
      .notify-input { border-right: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: none; }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .axis-track { animation: none; }
      .status-dot { animation: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <span class="nav-logo">GFD</span>
    <span class="nav-status">
      <span class="status-dot"></span>
      In development
    </span>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Game Feel Database</p>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">Games rated on<br /><em>how they feel,</em><br />not what they are.</h1>
    <p class="hero-body">
      Steam thinks Elden Ring and The Sims are similar games. They share a tag, so the algorithm agrees.<br /><br />
      GFD scores every game across <strong>25 axes</strong> (movement weight, cognitive load, penalty severity, narrative density) and uses those scores to surface recommendations that actually make sense.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <span class="cta-secondary">Database launching soon</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AXIS STRIP -->
  <div class="axis-strip" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="axis-track">
      <span class="axis-tag f">Movement Weight</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Traversal Richness</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Combat Pace</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Cognitive Load</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Tonal Register</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Moment-to-Moment Levity</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Narrative Density</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Player Agency</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Progression Meaningfulness</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Crafting Depth</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">World Reactivity</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Life Skills Depth</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Mechanical Expression</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Combat Difficulty</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Puzzle Difficulty</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Scarcity Pressure</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Knowledge Gap</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Penalty Severity</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">Character Customisation</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">Visual Character Design</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">Exploration Reward</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">FOMO Mechanics</span>
      <!-- duplicate for seamless loop -->
      <span class="axis-tag f">Movement Weight</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Traversal Richness</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Combat Pace</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Cognitive Load</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Tonal Register</span>
      <span class="axis-tag f">Moment-to-Moment Levity</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Narrative Density</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Player Agency</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Progression Meaningfulness</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Crafting Depth</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">World Reactivity</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Life Skills Depth</span>
      <span class="axis-tag s">Mechanical Expression</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Combat Difficulty</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Puzzle Difficulty</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Scarcity Pressure</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Knowledge Gap</span>
      <span class="axis-tag d">Penalty Severity</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">Character Customisation</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">Visual Character Design</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">Exploration Reward</span>
      <span class="axis-tag i">FOMO Mechanics</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <p class="step-num">01</p>
        <h3 class="step-title">Every game gets a profile</h3>
        <p class="step-body">Each game is scored across 25 axes by trained scorers. Not vibes. Specific mechanics. How heavy does movement feel? How punishing is failure? Does the story branch?</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <p class="step-num">02</p>
        <h3 class="step-title">You set what matters</h3>
        <p class="step-body">Toggle the axes you care about. Crank up Penalty Severity. Ignore everything else. The system finds games that match what you actually want, regardless of genre.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <p class="step-num">03</p>
        <h3 class="step-title">Recommendations explain themselves</h3>
        <p class="step-body">Every result tells you why it matched. Not "because you played X" but "similar weighty movement, similar slow narrative pace." Useful signal, not a black box.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PILLAR EXPLAINER -->
    <div style="margin-top: 5rem;">
      <p class="section-label">The four pillars</p>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <p class="pillar-name f">Feel</p>
          <p class="pillar-desc">How the game exists in your body and brain moment to moment: movement, pace, cognitive load, tone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <p class="pillar-name s">Systems</p>
          <p class="pillar-desc">How the game is architected underneath: narrative density, progression, crafting, world reactivity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <p class="pillar-name d">Difficulty</p>
          <p class="pillar-desc">A cross-cutting concern scored independently: combat, puzzles, resource scarcity, knowledge gaps, penalty severity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <p class="pillar-name i">Identity</p>
          <p class="pillar-desc">How much the game lets you make it yours: customisation, exploration reward, and whether it respects your time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NOTIFY -->
  <div class="notify-section">
    <div class="notify-inner">
      <h2 class="notify-headline">The database is coming.</h2>
      <p class="notify-sub">Leave your email and we'll let you know when it's live.</p>
      <div class="notify-form">
        <input class="notify-input" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" />
        <button class="notify-btn">Notify me</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <span class="footer-logo">Game Feel Database</span>
    <span class="footer-note">gamefeeldatabase.com</span>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
